des:
Use this Skill if you'd like to learn interesting facts about the renowned crypto-artist César Yagüe

César Yagüe (b. 1971) is a Spanish producer, creative director, 2D, 3D and VFX artist. Since 1993 he has been professionally dedicated to art within the world of communications. He has created multiple visual works of art for publicity, feature films, TV, Internet, events and installations.

To start, just say "Alexa, open Ambient Art" to get a fact".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
